Class BionicJoystick

  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BionicF310

    public class BionicJoystick
extends edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.Joystick
    BionicJoystick abstracts away much of the prior operator interface complexity to reduce the likelihood of confusion in button and axis mapping. All methods rely on BionicAxis and BionicButton objects defined in their respective controller's classes.
